---
title: Harissa Pork Stuffed Aubergine with Bulgur Wheat and Mint Yoghurt
description: This delicious Harissa Pork Stuffed Aubergine has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R26_W13_UK_L13264-3_Main_low-a8026abb.jpg
